<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>About | Trusted Household &amp; Childcare</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <section class="page-hero">
        <h1>About Trusted Household &amp; Childcare</h1>
        <p>Trusted international Filipino household and childcare staffing for families worldwide.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content">
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div>
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>Trusted Household &amp; Childcare was born from a clear need: international families deserve access to household and childcare professionals of the highest caliber, wherever in the world they are.</p>
                <p>We specialize in sourcing, vetting, and placing experienced Filipino household and childcare professionals — nannies, private chefs, and executive housekeepers — for families who expect nothing less than excellence.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>Our Approach</h2>
                <p>Every placement begins with understanding your family's unique needs, schedule, and household culture. We then draw from our curated network of pre-vetted professionals, each with verified experience and references from international placements.</p>
                <p>During consultation, we can discuss your family's requirements, candidate suitability, and local process considerations, and support a smooth introduction and onboarding — so you can focus on what matters.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-row">
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">500+</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Placements Made</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">7</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Priority Markets</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">98%</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Client Retention</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">24/7</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Support Available</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
